# Device Strategy

## Web

Vertical domains: `bourbon.foundryos.com`, `books.foundryos.com`, etc.

## Mobile

**Build Foundry app only.** Worlds inside: Bourbon, Movies, Books, BBQ, Genealogy.

Do NOT build Bourbon App, Movie App, Book App.

## One Graph

One install · one account · one notification system · one social/reputation/collection graph

## Offline (Future)

Download: collections, academy, encyclopedia, notes — `offline_sync_manifests` table ready.

See `docs/DEVICE_STRATEGY.md`, `docs/OFFLINE_SYNC.md`
